I"r<p>795 homes on Enfield’s Joyce Avenue and Snells Park estates have been earmarked for redevelopment in Hammersmith and Fulham’s <a href="https://www.lbhf.gov.uk/sites/default/files/section_attachments/local_plan_2018_web_version.pdf">Local Plan</a> (See Strategic Site Policy WCRA2).</p>

