<p>The Council is <a href="https://enfielddispatch.co.uk/major-estate-plans-to-go-to-vote/">reported</a> to be intending to hold a ballot some time in 2020. Its dedicated website for the scheme provides further details <a href="http://www.joyceandsnells.co.uk/">here</a>.</p>
